 <span data-ttu-id="ed7ed-144">应用程序可以自由地完全更改的值<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed7ed-144">Applications are free to completely change the value of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment.TextToSpeak%2A>.</span></span>  
  
