 <span data-ttu-id="ed7ed-147">的实现<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed7ed-147">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="ed7ed-148">接收实例的<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>数组，并创建`Speak`要在基础合成<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>引擎上传递给方法的新的实例数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ed7ed-148">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
